London has been trumped by New York as the best destination in the world for nightlife and shopping, according to new survey results.

The UK capital was ranked second and third place respectively, while the American city scooped first and second place.

However, Dubai squeezed them both out of the top spot for shopping to be crowned the best destination on the planet for buying goods while on holiday.

